prompts.frontCover:
Front cover of a greeting card, flat 2D illustration. In a vibrant watercolor style with soft edges and beautiful color bleeds, depict a humorous and charming beach scene.

Illustrated cartoon versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are the central focus. Lao Lao is playfully trying to build a giant sandcastle shaped like a boba tea drink, complete with a straw made of driftwood and "tapioca pearls" made of smooth, dark pebbles. She's laughing, maybe with a little bit of sand on her cheek, looking very happy. Lao Lao is wearing a light blue sweatshirt and black pants.

Jordan stands beside her, struggling comically to carry an oversized, comically large boba tea cup that's almost as big as he is. He has a playful, slightly exasperated expression as if the cup is very heavy. Jordan is wearing a tan hoodie and dark-colored pants.

The setting is a cute, stylized beach with gentle turquoise waves lapping at the shore. The sand is a soft, golden yellow. In the background, there are a few whimsical pastel-colored beach huts and cartoonish palm trees. The sky is a blend of soft blues, pinks, and yellows, suggesting a cheerful, sunny day.

Centered in the middle of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!". The text is placed in a clear area, with the main characters positioned slightly below it.
